description: “This is Feelings, a show about touching at the edges of the borders and boundaries of our lives, feeling out the frontiers and emotions and understandings that make meaning.” Feelings’ host, audio producer and mental health nurse Julia Murphy, explores the mind/body divide to help show how we each construct our own personal narratives.
